    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Anatoma tangaroa new species. Holotype, NW of Three Kings Islands, northern New Zealand, 188 m (NMNZ M. 303297). Scale bar shell = 1 mm. Scale bar protoconch = 100 µm." ;
